# Cloudflare Pages Redirects and Rewrites
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/platform/redirects/
#
# NOTE: The "/* /index.html 200" SPA rewrite rule is intentionally omitted here.
# Wrangler v3+ detects it as an infinite loop and silently drops it, leaving
# every non-asset route returning a 404.
# SPA routing is handled instead by:
#   1. functions/_middleware.ts  — serves index.html for non-API 404 responses
#   2. dist/404.html             — Cloudflare Pages serves 404.html for any miss
#      (generated by "cp dist/index.html dist/404.html" in the build script)
